article.description: — Ryan Schwieger had 22 points as Loyola Chicago easily defeated Chicago State 92-56 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Schwieger leads Loyola Chicago over Chicago St. 92-56
article.linkText: Schwieger leads Loyola Chicago over Chicago St. 92-56
article.story: CHICAGO -- — Ryan Schwieger had 22 points as Loyola Chicago easily defeated Chicago State 92-56 on Tuesday night. Jacob Hutson had 15 points for Loyola Chicago (3-0). Aher Uguak added 14 points. Tate Hall had seven rebounds. Brandon Betson had 21 points for the Cougars (2-1). Dominique Alexander added 10 points. Coreyoun Rushin had nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
